Avoid test failure with LLVM compilers due to either miscomplication
or misbehaving optimization on aarch64 specifically.

See https://github.com/OpenMathLib/OpenBLAS/issues/5532

Author: Jan Reuter (JSC)

diff --color -Naur OpenBLAS-0.3.30.orig/kernel/arm64/dot_kernel_asimd.c OpenBLAS-0.3.30/kernel/arm64/dot_kernel_asimd.c
